{"tid":2435410,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"香港不再獲美國傳統基金會經濟自由度評分　學者﹕影響有限","createTime":"2021-03-06T08:17:39.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-06T17:44:47.000Z","uid":46356,"like":8,"dislike":43,"uniUserReply":45,"replies":[{"pid":"5620e789830be323d6d47a74b193bbe9e1e306b4","tid":2435410,"uid":46356,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-06T08:17:39.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/%E8%B2%A1%E7%B6%93%E5%BF%AB%E8%A8%8A/594801/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F%25E8%25B2%25A1%25E7%25B6%2593%25E5%25BF%25AB%25E8%25A8%258A%2F594801%2F&d=vOSJ0XARgdQWnSR9BVy1n0YD92OErucUe%2F0sHRi%2FZkY%3D&h=68a91677\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/%E8%B2%A1%E7%B6%93%E5%BF%AB%E8%A8%8A/594801/</a><br />\n<br />\n香港不再獲美國傳統基金會經濟自由度評分 學者﹕影響有限<br />\n<br />\n撰文：張偉倫翟梓謙<br />\n2021-03-04 13:32<br />\n最後更新日期：2021-03-04 13:59<br />\n<br />\n美國傳統基金會在最新一份經濟自由度指數中，並無將香港給予獨立評分，而是將香港與澳門與中國一同評分。在最新排名，中國排第107位。在此之前，香港在該自由度指數一直是名列前矛，更曾連22年掛名第一。今次香港在評分榜中缺席，自然備受外界關注。不過學者認為，香港仍是經濟自由度相當高的地方，今次事件不會對本港營商環境及經濟自由情況造成影響，反而香港應在促進不干預別人的自由這方面作出努力。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20210304/444136095915970560094587.jpeg/t_8yqY6i7ATrRhS0fDPmQ6cGs5DA7GjmMlIGWjJSBlo?v=w1280\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2Fdw%2F20210304%2F444136095915970560094587.jpeg%2Ft_8yqY6i7ATrRhS0fDPmQ6cGs5DA7GjmMlIGWjJSBlo%3Fv%3Dw1280&h=b1edb317&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n雷鼎鳴認為香港不再獲基金會獨立評分，似是政治考量，所以作出評論的意義不大。（余俊亮攝）<br />\n<br />\n徐家健﹕對資本市場造成影響有限<br />\n<br />\n美國克林信大學經濟系副教授徐家健指，香港被剔出指數「唔係咩大不了嘅事」，始終學術界從來都不太重視這一類指數，因為這些指數的研究方法並不太科學化，只是覆蓋稅率居多，但關乎一些規管及壟斷的問題卻又未能反映。<br />\n<br />\n對於是次剔出香港，徐家健提出一些可能性，其一是在「一國兩制」變形走樣下，將香港納入研究範圍已沒有意思，香港已經是中國的一部分，正如指數無須為上海、北京制訂排名。其二是相對「陰謀論」的可能性，當近年該指數反映香港經濟愈漸不自由，排名持續向下，衍生更多相關的負面新聞，便受到一些「影響」，從而將香港剔除。<br />\n<br />\n他認為即使香港被剔出指數之外，對資本市場造成影響非常有限，「啲錢好醒目嘅，唔使靠呢啲指標去教佢哋做嘢」，資金本身已經有能力對投資作分析。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20210304/444136171853844480102674.jpeg/tEHeWrRiLPgXY9P50J1f7uUbJADbyaXa2TW3H9k1tx8?v=w1280\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2Fdw%2F20210304%2F444136171853844480102674.jpeg%2FtEHeWrRiLPgXY9P50J1f7uUbJADbyaXa2TW3H9k1tx8%3Fv%3Dw1280&h=24a19de2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n徐家健認為，今次香港被剔出指數「唔係咩大不了嘅事」。（羅國輝攝）"},{"pid":"d6c09a9f5e7f21bcea8dccc4f325196fe9f5585e","tid":2435410,"uid":51271,"like":22,"dislike":0,"score":22,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-03-06T08:18:41.000Z","msg":"支那01 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aaadd70bd78a12b3d612e12af84316eb9a010a21","tid":2435410,"uid":18477,"like":23,"dislike":0,"score":23,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-06T08:19:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><span class=\"red\"><span class=\"xx-large\"><strong>閪01死全家</strong></span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dfe8c58aceaa9f05bee7dd42ae2cd7d9c8aff08f","tid":2435410,"uid":244809,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-06T08:21:04.000Z","msg":"徐家健....我仲以為佢係黃同正常人<br />\n點知又係一個白痴"},{"pid":"063adb06c93737ac18462fcacd52ff2420c80cdc","tid":2435410,"uid":7369,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-06T08:22:31.000Z","msg":"徐家健鬼鬼地？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/think.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8982ffbafc0d36f207350f9ed40daf727644e66b","tid":2435410,"uid":83582,"like":17,"dislike":0,"score":17,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-06T08:23:22.000Z","msg":"雷鼎鳴 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2bdf589db4dd96bda554a22e1c5bf2a09a72cba6","tid":2435410,"uid":388108,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"d6c09a9f5e7f21bcea8dccc4f325196fe9f5585e","tid":2435410,"uid":51271,"like":22,"dislike":0,"score":22,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-03-06T08:18:41.000Z","msg":"支那01 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-06T08:26:27.000Z","msg":"仲以為係陳偉強㖭"},{"pid":"9cbe83e1a48d96e3d328fba3da51434564a3cb86","tid":2435410,"uid":156652,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-06T08:26:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/o4C9K5d.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fo4C9K5d.gif&h=63624ee4&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"90fc2584608a5768e7c507c4d45b0c9aefb1f365","tid":2435410,"uid":53062,"like":22,"dislike":0,"score":22,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-03-06T08:27:42.000Z","msg":"年年用來打飛機，跟住話其實唔重要<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8ffdd91de4c8568bdc523eb7452cfbc4ecc9d83b","tid":2435410,"uid":89184,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-06T08:28:00.000Z","msg":"學者<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e9fc6bb7532b4466aa02e4445fcfe6d01d93c048","tid":2435410,"uid":58335,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-06T08:28:28.000Z","msg":"雷鼎鳴<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8875cdce94b33b27fb7a4acbc97573580ebe7c0f","tid":2435410,"uid":13503,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-06T08:30:53.000Z","msg":"如果學者咁把炮今日世界首富應該全部都係學者"},{"pid":"56614c8dc2a7b59bb470f2cd52f8a085096d3f70","tid":2435410,"uid":71175,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-06T08:33:19.000Z","msg":"雷鼎鳴 次次都9 UP"},{"pid":"7e96cf59faa4e485f1a4a2999e32643e7e25caa0","tid":2435410,"uid":522,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-06T08:35:55.000Z","msg":"學者：有大灣區就夠"},{"pid":"28100ff7ed8fe58c0511605bd8aa33af50141845","tid":2435410,"uid":57309,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-06T08:37:38.000Z","msg":"學者<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"482c25f36f175b3cacf8f2c137884d3b906916be","tid":2435410,"uid":85629,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-06T08:39:16.000Z","msg":"始終學術界從來都不太重視這一類指數<br />\n<br />\n真係戇鳩鳩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />做生意點同"},{"pid":"650605ce453d9ecf5d18501f032d4bb3f3d32bb2","tid":2435410,"uid":364767,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-06T08:45:38.000Z","msg":"若果真係『影響有限』仲洗乜搵你出嚟鳩噏<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d3e8bfdc1da6062d327ef4ef81e21ccb46d9fbf7","tid":2435410,"uid":271199,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-06T08:52:36.000Z","msg":"咩學者呀 ？ 有冇咩著名論文呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/zzz.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0f30d959515da3623df29da8fd20e98a11f34ec1","tid":2435410,"uid":263577,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"90fc2584608a5768e7c507c4d45b0c9aefb1f365","tid":2435410,"uid":53062,"like":22,"dislike":0,"score":22,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-03-06T08:27:42.000Z","msg":"年年用來打飛機，跟住話其實唔重要<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-06T08:56:51.000Z","msg":"戒丁<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eed040dacea099db286a0fe18f12cbde98351a26","tid":2435410,"uid":22422,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-06T10:18:32.000Z","msg":"由第2變107都叫冇影響<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/tea.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/tea.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"667b5f2ff0725f33ba08534f4decd4d53168d6e0","tid":2435410,"uid":26770,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d3e8bfdc1da6062d327ef4ef81e21ccb46d9fbf7","tid":2435410,"uid":271199,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-06T08:52:36.000Z","msg":"咩學者呀 ？ 有冇咩著名論文呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/zzz.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-06T11:08:08.000Z","msg":"徐家健教授畢業於芝加哥大學經濟系，在美國克林信大學取得終生教席，是香港中文大學亞太研究所經濟研究中心成員，以及中南財經政法大學的特聘教授。徐教授亦曾在香港大學、香港中文大學、香港科技大學、香港理工大學、香港金融研究中心、新加坡國立大 學、以及比利時魯汶大學訪問。他的論文曾發表在《美國經濟學報：宏觀經濟》、《經濟學報》、《金融中介學報》等十多份國際學術期刊。除了研究及教學，徐教授也有參與私人經濟顧問的工作，和參與公職服務如香港電台節目顧問團成員、政府劃房研究工作小組 員及廣東核電站第十一屆核安全咨詢委員會委員,他亦是《信報》、《信報月刊》、《am730》及《蘋果日報》的專欄作者。<br />\n-------------<br />\n<span class=\"red\">徐家健又係埋堆搏上岸果班人</span>"},{"pid":"29069e6f52649fdc109d86ad7ad802ebe8afca74","tid":2435410,"uid":266170,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"5620e789830be323d6d47a74b193bbe9e1e306b4","tid":2435410,"uid":46356,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-06T08:17:39.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/%E8%B2%A1%E7%B6%93%E5%BF%AB%E8%A8%8A/594801/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F%25E8%25B2%25A1%25E7%25B6%2593%25E5%25BF%25AB%25E8%25A8%258A%2F594801%2F&d=vOSJ0XARgdQWnSR9BVy1n0YD92OErucUe%2F0sHRi%2FZkY%3D&h=68a91677\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/%E8%B2%A1%E7%B6%93%E5%BF%AB%E8%A8%8A/594801/</a><br />\n<br />\n香港不再獲美國傳統基金會經濟自由度評分 學者﹕影響有限<br />\n<br />\n撰文：張偉倫翟梓謙<br />\n2021-03-04 13:32<br />\n最後更新日期：2021-03-04 13:59<br />\n<br />\n美國傳統基金會在最新一份經濟自由度指數中，並無將香港給予獨立評分，而是將香港與澳門與中國一同評分。在最新排名，中國排第107位。在此之前，香港在該自由度指數一直是名列前矛，更曾連22年掛名第一。今次香港在評分榜中缺席，自然備受外界關注。不過學者認為，香港仍是經濟自由度相當高的地方，今次事件不會對本港營商環境及經濟自由情況造成影響，反而香港應在促進不干預別人的自由這方面作出努力。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20210304/444136095915970560094587.jpeg/t_8yqY6i7ATrRhS0fDPmQ6cGs5DA7GjmMlIGWjJSBlo?v=w1280\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2Fdw%2F20210304%2F444136095915970560094587.jpeg%2Ft_8yqY6i7ATrRhS0fDPmQ6cGs5DA7GjmMlIGWjJSBlo%3Fv%3Dw1280&h=b1edb317&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n雷鼎鳴認為香港不再獲基金會獨立評分，似是政治考量，所以作出評論的意義不大。（余俊亮攝）<br />\n<br />\n徐家健﹕對資本市場造成影響有限<br />\n<br />\n美國克林信大學經濟系副教授徐家健指，香港被剔出指數「唔係咩大不了嘅事」，始終學術界從來都不太重視這一類指數，因為這些指數的研究方法並不太科學化，只是覆蓋稅率居多，但關乎一些規管及壟斷的問題卻又未能反映。<br />\n<br />\n對於是次剔出香港，徐家健提出一些可能性，其一是在「一國兩制」變形走樣下，將香港納入研究範圍已沒有意思，香港已經是中國的一部分，正如指數無須為上海、北京制訂排名。其二是相對「陰謀論」的可能性，當近年該指數反映香港經濟愈漸不自由，排名持續向下，衍生更多相關的負面新聞，便受到一些「影響」，從而將香港剔除。<br />\n<br />\n他認為即使香港被剔出指數之外，對資本市場造成影響非常有限，「啲錢好醒目嘅，唔使靠呢啲指標去教佢哋做嘢」，資金本身已經有能力對投資作分析。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20210304/444136171853844480102674.jpeg/tEHeWrRiLPgXY9P50J1f7uUbJADbyaXa2TW3H9k1tx8?v=w1280\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2Fdw%2F20210304%2F444136171853844480102674.jpeg%2FtEHeWrRiLPgXY9P50J1f7uUbJADbyaXa2TW3H9k1tx8%3Fv%3Dw1280&h=24a19de2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n徐家健認為，今次香港被剔出指數「唔係咩大不了嘅事」。（羅國輝攝）"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-06T11:23:12.000Z","msg":"【明報專訊】繼去年是25年來首次失落「全球最自由經濟體」第一位後，香港在美國傳統基金會公布的新一期經濟自由度指數中，首度被剔出名單。基金會稱主要因本港經濟政策明顯受中央控制；基金會創辦人形容，香港過去兩年失去政治自由和自主，致與其他中國城市如上海、北京無異。特區政府昨晚發聲明指對基金會決定表示極度失望和遺憾，認為是政治上有偏見及偏離以往一貫做法；有經濟學者認為，排名來自美國的智庫，對本港實際影響不大。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.mingpao.com/pns/%e6%b8%af%e8%81%9e/article/20210305/s00002/1614883558224/%e5%82%b3%e7%b5%b1%e5%9f%ba%e9%87%91%e6%9c%83%e6%8c%87%e6%b8%af%e7%b6%93%e6%bf%9f%e6%94%bf%e7%ad%96%e5%8f%97%e4%b8%ad%e5%a4%ae%e6%8e%a7%e5%88%b6-%e7%b6%93%e6%bf%9f%e8%87%aa%e7%94%b1%e6%8e%92%e5%90%8d%e5%89%94%e8%b5%b0%e9%a6%99%e6%b8%af\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fpns%2F%25e6%25b8%25af%25e8%2581%259e%2Farticle%2F20210305%2Fs00002%2F1614883558224%2F%25e5%2582%25b3%25e7%25b5%25b1%25e5%259f%25ba%25e9%2587%2591%25e6%259c%2583%25e6%258c%2587%25e6%25b8%25af%25e7%25b6%2593%25e6%25bf%259f%25e6%2594%25bf%25e7%25ad%2596%25e5%258f%2597%25e4%25b8%25ad%25e5%25a4%25ae%25e6%258e%25a7%25e5%2588%25b6-%25e7%25b6%2593%25e6%25bf%259f%25e8%2587%25aa%25e7%2594%25b1%25e6%258e%2592%25e5%2590%258d%25e5%2589%2594%25e8%25b5%25b0%25e9%25a6%2599%25e6%25b8%25af&d=vOSJ0XARgdQWnSR9BVy1n0YD92OErucUe%2F0sHRi%2FZkY%3D&h=032bbc6e\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fpns%2F%25e6%25b8%25af%25e8%2581%259e%2Farticle%2F20210305%2Fs00002%2F1614883558224%2F%25e5%2582%25b3%25e7%25b5%25b1%25e5%259f%25ba%25e9%2587%2591%25e6%259c%2583%25e6%258c%2587%25e6%25b8%25af%25e7%25b6%2593%25e6%25bf%259f%25e6%2594%25bf%25e7%25ad%2596%25e5%258f%2597%25e4%25b8%25ad%25e5%25a4%25ae%25e6%258e%25a7%25e5%2588%25b6-%25e7%25b6%2593%25e6%25bf%259f%25e8%2587%25aa%25e7%2594%25b1%25e6%258e%2592%25e5%2590%258d%25e5%2589%2594%25e8%25b5%25b0%25e9%25a6%2599%25e6%25b8%25af&h=8452d64f\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.mingpao.com/pns/%e6%b8%af%e8%81%9e/article/20210305/s00002/1614883558224/%e5%82%b3%e7%b5%b1%e5%9f%ba%e9%87%91%e6%9c%83%e6%8c%87%e6%b8%af%e7%b6%93%e6%bf%9f%e6%94%bf%e7%ad%96%e5%8f%97%e4%b8%ad%e5%a4%ae%e6%8e%a7%e5%88%b6-%e7%b6%93%e6%bf%9f%e8%87%aa%e7%94%b1%e6%8e%92%e5%90%8d%e5%89%94%e8%b5%b0%e9%a6%99%e6%b8%af</a><br />\n<br />\n...<br />\n<br />\n<strong>學者：信貸評級若看齊中國影響更大</strong><br />\n美國克林信大學經濟學系副教授徐家健表示，香港被剔出傳統基金會的名單，對本港的實際影響不大，他稱有關指數來自美國智庫，而不是來自銀行或金融機構，指其參考範疇一向未夠全面，例如未有參考政府如何監管市場壟斷行為等。<br />\n<br />\n徐續稱，學術界與外資大都不會參考該指數，稱外資對本港的投資信心，主要取決於本港的法治、資金是否自由出入等實際因素。<strong>但徐提醒，若國際評級機構也將香港評級跟中國內地看齊，屆時將真正影響本港公司的信貸評級，影響極大。</strong>"},{"pid":"2f8c599368f6a42750690fbb6ed03778ec1e85cb","tid":2435410,"uid":290118,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-06T11:25:54.000Z","msg":"磚家食屎啦.jpg"},{"pid":"4cb98d0b60e62590906ae9dbaa0e5386fecd3355","tid":2435410,"uid":54161,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-06T11:34:05.000Z","msg":"對於是次剔出香港，徐家健提出一些可能性，其一是在「一國兩制」變形走樣下，將香港納入研究範圍已沒有意思，香港已經是中國的一部分，正如指數無須為上海、北京制訂排名。<span class=\"red\">其二是相對「陰謀論」的可能性，當近年該指數反映香港經濟愈漸不自由，排名持續向下，衍生更多相關的負面新聞，便受到一些「影響」，從而將香港剔除。</span><br />\n<br />\n暗示受到中國壓力不如成個香港唔計<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n同其他城市一視同仁"},{"pid":"ca88c2ae15c5d2fa63f948aa769ef9250552cdef","tid":2435410,"uid":46356,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"eed040dacea099db286a0fe18f12cbde98351a26","tid":2435410,"uid":22422,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-06T10:18:32.000Z","msg":"由第2變107都叫冇影響<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/tea.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/tea.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-06T12:46:13.000Z","msg":"所以學者一開始就首先定性個排名表都係公信力同冇用<br />\n咁就算由1跌到10000000都可以講係冇影響"}]}